# Frontend role

**May edit:** `apps/app/`, `packages/ui/src/`

**May not edit:** `apps/api/`, `packages/contracts/`

**Must:** Zustand for product state, `@kloqra/ui` primitives, `@kloqra/web-shared` for shared app code, and tests with every feature (`packages/ui` → `*.spec.tsx`, app `features/` → Playwright e2e or unit spec)
